I think that's why I ended it.

104
00:06:56,050 --> 00:06:57,620
你不允许自己害怕吗
And you have no room for fear?

105
00:06:58,150 --> 00:07:00,320
不  害怕成不了事
No. Being afraid doesn't accomplish anything.

106
00:07:00,940 --> 00:07:03,190
不对  我在海外时
That's not true. When I'm overseas,

107
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:05,540
合理的恐惧  像对疾病  暴力
rational fear... disease or violence...

108
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,490
这种恐惧让你生存下去
that sort of fear keeps you alive.

109
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:11,060
回到这儿  老天
Back here, God,

110
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:14,070
我感觉自己害怕些
I find myself afraid of things

111
00:07:14,530 --> 00:07:16,590
虚无缥缈的东西
