就比如  我有多渺小
It's like, uh, how little am I seeing?

113
00:07:20,890 --> 00:07:24,110
或者我是不是浪费了此时此日
Or have I wasted this day or this moment?

114
00:07:24,710 --> 00:07:26,400
是啊  我有时也会想
Yeah, I think that sometimes...

115
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,440
我的人生到底有没有意义
whether my life will add up.

116
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:33,620
弗兰西斯听到我说这些
Francis would roll his eyes

117
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:35,240
一定会翻白眼
if he heard me talking like this.

118
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:40,000
