Does he know where you are?

119
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,620
不知道
No, he doesn't.

120
00:07:54,410 --> 00:07:56,300
如果他在找你  你就在那儿
If he's looking for you, that's where you are.

121
00:07:57,230 --> 00:07:58,110
那里
Over there.

122
00:07:59,970 --> 00:08:01,020
你遇见弗兰克之前
Before you met Frank.

123
00:08:02,290 --> 00:08:03,270
独自一人
Alone.

124
00:08:03,970 --> 00:08:04,990
充满好奇
Curious.

125
00:08:05,900 --> 00:08:07,150
接纳一切事物
Absorbing everything.

126
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,080
你才不知道我年轻时是什么样的
You have no idea what I was like when I was a girl.

127
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,590
他知道你的那一面吗
Did he ever know that side of you?

128
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,590
他对那女孩不感兴趣
He wasn't interested in that girl.

129
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,960
我也是
And neither was I.

130
00:08:23,810 --> 00:08:25,180
那你对什么感兴趣
What were you interested in?

131
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:27,130
不仅是观察别人
Being more than an observer.

132
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,590
你想受人瞩目
You wanted to be seen.

133
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:31,840
不只是受到瞩目
Not just seen.

134
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,340
我要举足轻重
I wanted to be significant.

135
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:44,240
历史上没有先例
There's no historical precedent.

136
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:45,980
